1) Building GHDL with LLVM:
    - If git not present: "sudo apt install git"
    - Create a temporary directory <ghdl> and:
        - "git clone https://github.com/ghdl/ghdl.git"
    - Install GNAT: "sudo apt-get install gnat"
    - Install llvm: "sudo apt install llvm"
    - Install make: "sudo apt install make"
    - Install clang: "sudo apt-get install clang"
    - Install libz-dev: "sudo apt-get install libz-dev"
    - GCC installation may also be needed: "sudo apt-get install gcc"
    - Then: 
            $ cd <ghdl>
            $ mkdir build
            $ cd build
            $ ../configure --with-llvm-config --prefix=/usr/local
            $ make
            $ sudo make install

2) Python3
    - Install Python3 if needed: "sudo apt-get install python3"
    - Install pip: "sudo apt install python3-pip"
    - Install dependencies: "sudo pip3 install flask flask_socketio flask-login flask-sqlalchemy flask-migrate yagmail psycopg2"

3) FPGAEmuWeb 
    - Clone with git: "git clone https://gitlab.com/dudubatista/fpgaemuweb.git"
    - get back to FPGAEmuWeb dir and run the server: "python3 start.py"
    